The libemf library provides functionality for reading and writing Enhanced Metafile (EMF) files.

## Usage

### CMake
```cmake
find_package(libemf REQUIRED)
target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE libemf::libemf)
```

### pkg-config
```bash
pkg-config --cflags --libs libemf
```

## Features

- **tools**: Build EMF conversion tools (emf2svg, emf2eps, etc.)
  - Install with: `vcpkg install libemf[tools]`

## Example

```cpp
#include <libemf/libemf.h>

// 创建EMF文件
EMF *emf = emf_create();
if (emf) {
    // 添加绘图命令
    emf_rectangle(emf, 10, 10, 100, 100);
    
    // 保存文件
    emf_save(emf, "output.emf");
    emf_destroy(emf);
}
```

## Notes

- This library is primarily designed for Windows EMF file format support
- The tools feature provides command-line utilities for EMF file conversion
- Static linking is recommended for better compatibility
